---
title: Seared Steak & Creamy Parmesan Sauce with Oven-Baked Chips & Greens
description: There’s something eternally comforting about the aroma of herbs and garlic bubbling in a creamy Parmesan sauce. Completely mouth-watering to say the least. Drizzled over tender seared steak with a side of greens and oven-baked chips, it’s time for pub-style steak and chips to move over; there’s a new contender in town.
